scopecontent.p:
Locations include but are not limited to: the city of Jaffa (Tel Aviv); Sea of Galilee;
        Jerusalem; Bethlehem; Mount of Temptation (identified with Mount Quarantania); Jericho;
        Jordan River; Mount Hermon; Bethsaida; Mount of Olives; Emmaus (El- Kubebeh); the mosaic
        floor at Beit Jibrin; River Abana (El-Barada); Tyre; and the Temple of Sethos. There are
        also two glass slides with maps of ancient Middle East and Palestine. Five of the slides are
        damaged and are filed at the end of the collection.
